                    <div class="description">
                        Have an upcoming presentation and you are already stressing out?
                        Let's add this event so we dont forget and we'll give you helpful tools you need
                        to crush it!
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="extra content">

                    <span>
                        <i class="question icon"></i>
                        <a id="presentation-prep"
                            href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/specific-phobias/expert-answers/fear-of-public-speaking/faq-20058416">Quick
                            Facts about Presentation anxiety</a>
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="./styles/img/networking.jpeg">
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <div class="header">Networking Event</div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-info" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#networking">Add
                        Event</button>

                    <div class="description">
                        Looking to branch out for a new job or new friends? Networking events are great for gaining
                        social skills
                        and practicing elevator pitches! If you're nervous don't sweat it, add this event and we'll
                        go
                        step-by-step before your networking day.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="extra content">

                    <span>
                        <i class="question icon"></i>
                        <a href="https://www.themuse.com/advice/9-tips-for-navigating-your-first-networking-event">Things
                            to Consider</a>
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="./styles/img/interview.jpg">
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <div class="header">Interview time!</div>

                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-info" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#interview">Add
                        Event</button>



                    <div class="description">
                        Interviews are nerve wrecking for everyone, with us, we give you the best tips/tricks to
                        remember
                        so you dont go in there feeling it's you against the company...we got <strong>YOUR</strong>
                        back.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="extra content">

                    <span>
                        <i class="question icon"></i>
                        <a href="https://www.experisjobs.us/exp_us/en/career-advice/20-tips-job-interviews.htm">Body
                            language and more!</a>
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
